data.description: Beautifully remodeled home with 4 beds 3.5 baths on the Southside of Eau Claire. Walking distance to parks, schools and shopping. As you walk into this gorgeous home you will see the quality of work that has been completed to make this the perfect home for you. From refinished hardwood floors, new light fixtures, paint and opening up the entry way to make you feel right at home. The kitchen remodel was completed to make your life easier in your new home with a great floor plan, new stainless steel appliances, large stainless steel kitchen sink, granite counter tops, a plethora of beautiful cabinets. This home has extra space that can be used for a classroom setting, gym, office or craft room. Relax with friends and family in the spacious family room or theater room or out on the patio under a starry night.
